{"tid":2508451,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人打pes打撚到又灰又忟?","createTime":"2021-04-28T19:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:35:43.000Z","uid":340063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f36d14d1a84db1614dab8ee06348c36d3852b0","tid":2508451,"uid":340063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:03:33.000Z","msg":"啲人永遠唔撚識迎波<br />\n猜幾腳就甩晒<br />\n難得揾到空位吊個波單刀啦<br />\n唔係俾人撞走就係拉停<br />\n成個game喺度鬥撞<br />\n但進攻防守都係永遠撞輸<br />\n連牙朗都撞唔贏比利連<br />\n打反擊嗰時中場拎波推進<br />\n啲翼鋒可以停喺度唔撚郁既<br />\n美斯數值有102 唔知點解可以咁樣走位<br />\n咁點樣反擊姐<br />\n仲有啲迫害我嘅中柱呢<br />\n打legend啲97+球員都變哂弱智咁<br />\n平時走位傳波都唔係好㗎啦<br />\n一打難啲成班就好似弱智仔 咁我點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab48433c81aaa7a632d0e57bdc4772973b3ac3d","tid":2508451,"uid":368336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:12:21.000Z","msg":"全部都經歷過 仲有唔可以cancel動作 d人on99咁有delay <br />\n而家學識左鳩咁玩就贏"},{"pid":"6cc8470d27e6857a11211d3b881ec6b50856602b","tid":2508451,"uid":340063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab48433c81aaa7a632d0e57bdc4772973b3ac3d","tid":2508451,"uid":368336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:12:21.000Z","msg":"全部都經歷過 仲有唔可以cancel動作 d人on99咁有delay <br />\n而家學識左鳩咁玩就贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"當你諗住第一時間清波/猜返定 <br />\n然後一下delay就俾人偷走/遮線<br />\n之後就on99失波了"},{"pid":"3295ac8fa3e07df4114b4f30cfed3a2804ab6789","tid":2508451,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T20:13:34.000Z","msg":"我試過嬲到掟爛部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5661e838e871ab4ede33f7078d93a4a0a94a7e","tid":2508451,"uid":16113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T20:37:57.000Z","msg":"仲有電腦罰球準撚到<br />\n<br />\n雖然自己都好易射"},{"pid":"34aae9a19fd30965a3c4041fdc79849975034a3d","tid":2508451,"uid":369322,"like":0,"dislike":