-04-28T21:21:43.000Z","msg":"最頂唔順電腦喺後場猜波<br />\n明明佢落後緊<br />\n兩個後衛至少互傳三四腳再傳返俾個龍<br />\n然後再傳俾第二邊後衛再猜過<br />\n好似玩9你咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋隻game啲過人招數大部份對住電腦都係冇用<br />\n有招用後腳90度過人<br />\n㩒左掣之後你個球員都未郁<br />\n對面後衛好似偷睇到你㩒左咩掣咁<br />\n即刻封左你個位先<br />\n<br />\n我有時覺得我㩒左掣之後<br />\n電腦啲球員反應仲快過我自己啲球員"},{"pid":"55f4995e964360a5fce8e6e61216f4eda2a8d0fc","tid":2508451,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd26eb179abd4b62f54905fa5697bc9cb402e5e4","tid":2508451,"uid":340063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3295ac8fa3e07df4114b4f30cfed3a2804ab6789","tid":2508451,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T20:13:34.000Z","msg":"我試過嬲到掟爛部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T20:56:54.000Z","msg":"我都想掟手制，不過無錢買過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:43:37.000Z","msg":"我一集爛一隻手制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已棄game<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658100a490c3c3983310bbc78ac766f3d0e54a09","tid":2508451,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:51:01.000Z","msg":"落街踢好過啦"},{"pid":"16c330de2af8cd6886b103f39199860d2fa55732","tid":2508451,"uid":340063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658100a490c3c3983310bbc78ac766f3d0e54a09","tid":2508451,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T22:51:01.000Z","msg":"落街踢好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"好難約齊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}